13: // erroredProvider is a stub provider that is used in place of a provider that
14: // failed the configuration step. Within the context of Stacks, an errored
15: // provider would have been configured by Stacks, and therefore should not be
16: // configured again, or used for any offline functionality.
17: type erroredProvider struct{}
18: 
19: var _ providers.Interface = &erroredProvider{}
